cat <<EOF
minecraft-server-wrapper has been installed as a systemd service.

To start/stop minecraft-server-wrapper:

sudo systemctl start minecraft-server-wrapper
sudo systemctl stop minecraft-server-wrapper

To enable/disable minecraft-server-wrapper starting automatically on boot:

sudo systemctl enable minecraft-server-wrapper
sudo systemctl disable minecraft-server-wrapper

To reload minecraft-server-wrapper:

sudo systemctl restart minecraft-server-wrapper

To view minecraft-server-wrapper logs:

journalctl -f -u minecraft-server-wrapper

EOF